data.title: Looking for Richard - Full Cast & Crew
data.meta_description: Learn more about the full cast of Looking for Richard with news, photos, videos and more at TV Guide
data.text:
1996

1 hr 49 mins

Documentary, Drama

PG13

Watchlist

Where to Watch

Al Pacino produced, directed and stars in this behind-the-scenes look at the production of 'Richard III,' examining the struggle of cast and crew as they tackle Shakespeare's tale of the power-hungry monarch. Harris Yulin, Penelope Allen, Alec Baldwin, Kevin Spacey, Estelle Parsons, Winona Ryder, Aidan Quinn.
